    Class Description
    Application
    Main program for the Acumos Federation Gateway Server.
    Artifact
    Artifact enhanced with file name.
    BadRequestException
    Exception to abort current processing and reply to the peer with the specified HTTP response code and message.
    BasicAuthConfig
    Configuration for basic authentication credentials.
    Catalog
    Catalog enhanced with number of contained solutions.
    CatalogService
    API for accessing catalogs and related items.
    CatalogServiceImpl
    Service bean for implementing the Catalog service using Acumos CDS.
    ClientBase
    Base class for building clients.
    ClientBase.MapperBuilder
    Builder for mappers supporting parsing extended classes with extra fields.
    ClientConfig
    Configuration for a client.
    ClientMocking
    Simulate responses from Federation Gateway or other RestTemplate based clients.
    ClientMocking.RequestInfo
    Information on request being processed
    Clients
    Defines all beans used to access outside services.
    ContentService
    API for accessing content of artifacts and documents
    ContentServiceImpl
    Service bean for implementing the ContentService using Nexus and Docker.
    DockerConfig
    Configuration bean for Docker access parameters.
    Document
    Document enhanced with file name.
    FederationClient
    Client for the Federation Server's public (E5) API.
    FederationConfig
    Configuration bean for the external server in the Acumos Federation Gateway plus gateway-wide parameters.
    FederationController
    Controller bean for the external (public) API.
    FederationServer
    Define controller and configuration beans for the external (federation) server.
    GatewayClient
    Client for the Federation Gateway's private API.
    GatewayController
    Controller bean for the internal (gateway) API.
    GatewayServer
    Define controller and configuration beans for the internal (gateway) server.
    JsonResponse<T>
    Wrapper for Federation REST responses.
    ModelDataController
    ModelDataController for sending logging data sent from models - this controller has two purposes handling logs for - AI model parameter updates - Model usage logging
    NexusClient
    Client for accessing the Nexus server.
    NexusConfig
    Configuration bean for Nexus server access parameters.
    PeerModelDataController
    Provides an interface for the local Acumos peer to send model data out to the respective remote peer.
    PeerService
    API for accessing information about peers and related items.
    PeerServiceImpl
    Service bean for implementing the peer service using CDS.
    Security
    Service bean implementing authentication and peer identification services on requests to the Federation Gateway.
    Security.Peer
    Principal specifying identity and permissions of a user.
    ServerConfig
    Configuration bean for the internal and external servers in the Acumos Federation Gateway.
    ServerConfig.Server
    Configuration bean for the server port number
    ServiceConfig
    Configuration bean for services used by the Acumos Federation Gateway.
    Solution
    Solution enhanced to add revisions and picture.
    SolutionRevision
    Revision enhanced with artifacts, documents, and description.
    SubscriptionPoller
    Service bean for periodic polling of subscriptions to other peer's catalogs.
    TlsConfig
    Configuration for a TLS (https) client.
    TlsConfigException
    Exception thrown when an error occurs setting up TLS for a RestTemplate.
